@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM SAP Feature Flags (FF) - Component Architecture

actor "Business Application" as App
actor "DevOps / Admin" as Admin

node "Feature Flags Service Runtime" {
  component "FFServer\n(vibe.d REST API)" as Api
  component "FFService\n(Evaluation Engine +\nCRUD + Export/Import)" as Domain
  database "FFStore\n(In-Memory Data)" as Store
}

App --> Api : evaluate flags,\nquery flag state
Admin --> Api : create/update/delete flags,\ntoggle, export/import,\ndashboard
Api --> Domain : routed use-case operations
Domain --> Store : persist/retrieve flag data

note right of Domain
Capabilities:
- Boolean flags (on/off)
- String flags (multi-variation)
- Direct delivery (identifier targeting)
- Percentage delivery (weighted rollout)
- Export / import all flags
- Tenant-scoped multitenancy
- Dashboard analytics
end note

@enduml
